    "Id": "chassisdef_valiant_V4-LNT-J3",
    "Name": "Valiant",
    "Details": "The version designed by Margaret Florence for Johnston Industries is powered by an imported 210 light fusion engine and redesigns the right forearm into a full-fledged small shield. An flamer in the same arm provides anti-infantry support while heavy ferro-fibrous armor also addresses the concerns of MechWarriors who wanted more protection, though at the cost of the MASC. Finally, a trio of ER small lasers join the existing ER mediums to improve the J3's offensive capability.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Short</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>",
